\n\"Mixed people are the best people\"\n\n\n\nYeah, we're the best people \n because we're not too black or too white \n we're just the right mix \n we're the best of both worlds \n\nwe're the ones who can pass for white \nwhen we need to \nbut we're also black enough to be down with the struggle \n\nwe're the perfect balance \nwe're not too much of anything \nand that's what makes us the best people